overview_description.description:
Earth5R is a cutting-edge sustainability technology platform that brings people together, encouraging them to work together to take meaningful steps towards sustainability. 

Earth5R is a community-driven platform where citizens take action to drive environmental sustainability. While Governments, NGOs and Corporates will pledge support to ESG and Net Zero/ Carbon Neutral, we at Earth5R firmly believe that every individual needs to proactively contribute to sustainability goals to realize a long-term, meaningful impact. We are a community of 90,000+ volunteers across 50+ countries and our ground-level work has been accredited/awarded by UNESCO Green citizen, Paris Peace Forum and United Nations.
 
To make this initiative truly scalable, we synthesized our learnings over the last 8 years and launched a digital platform in Jan 2023. The digital platform encourages and enables citizens to collaborate, share ideas, volunteer, conduct events, do internships, take action and drive sustainability at grass root levels in any part of the world and at any point in time. The platform allows citizens to build a ‘Sustainability Portfolio’ which is a digitally verified compilation of all activities/efforts completed in a lifetime to restore the earth.
